♪ NOW I HAVE YOU... ♪

109
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:03,493
TORI:
♪ COME, WE MUST GO ♪

110
00:04:03,577 --> 00:04:04,536
DAVE AND TRISTAN:
♪ DON'T NEED ANYTHING AT ALL ♪

111
00:04:04,620 --> 00:04:07,789
