MORE SPONTANEOUS.

116
00:04:16,924 --> 00:04:20,010
DAVE:
FINE. I'M NOT IN THE MOOD
TO GET ALL LOVEY DOVEY ANYWAYS.

117
00:04:22,054 --> 00:04:24,473
TORI:
ARE YOU REALLY GONNA DO THE SHOW
WITHOUT REHEARSING THE KISS?

118
00:04:24,556 --> 00:04:27,017
